## Task Chain (7 tasks across 3 queues)

```
[SCRAPE queue]                [PROCESS queue]              [EMBED queue]
      в”Ӯ                              в”Ӯ                           в”Ӯ
scrape_topic                         в”Ӯ                           в”Ӯ
  в”Ӯ  Queries ArXiv API               в”Ӯ                           в”Ӯ
  в”Ӯ  Filters dedup                   в”Ӯ                           в”Ӯ
  в””в”Җв–ә scrape_paper_metadata          в”Ӯ                           в”Ӯ
        в”Ӯ  Fetches full metadata     в”Ӯ                           в”Ӯ
        в””в”Җв–ә download_pdf             в”Ӯ                           в”Ӯ
              в”Ӯ  HTTP stream PDF     в”Ӯ                           в”Ӯ
              в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв–ә parse_pdf                       в”Ӯ
                                   в”Ӯ  PyMuPDF section extract    в”Ӯ
                                   в””в”Җв–ә clean_text                в”Ӯ
                                         в”Ӯ  Strip boilerplate    в”Ӯ
                                         в””в”Җв–ә chunk_document      в”Ӯ
                                               в”Ӯ  512-tok chunks  в”Ӯ
                                               в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв–ә generate_embeddings
                                                                 в”Ӯ  Batch embed API
                                                                 в””в”Җв–ә store_chunks
                                                                       в”Ӯ  Write vectors
                                                                       в””в”Җв–ә mark_as_processed
```

## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Copy env template
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env вҖ” set OPENAI_API_KEY (or switch to EMBEDDING_PROVIDER=local)

# 2. Start everything
docker compose up -d

# 3. Watch tasks in Flower
open http://localhost:5555/flower

# 4. Manually trigger a scrape
docker compose exec worker-scrape \
    python scripts/trigger_scrape.py --topics cs.CL --max-results 20

# 5. Re-ingest a specific paper
docker compose exec worker-scrape \
    python scripts/trigger_scrape.py --arxiv-id 2401.12345
```

## Scaling

```bash
# Add more scrape workers when queue depth is high
docker compose up -d --scale worker-scrape=4

# Add more process workers for PDF-heavy workloads
docker compose up -d --scale worker-process=4

# Embed workers stay at 1вҖ“2 to respect API rate limits
docker compose up -d --scale worker-embed=2
```

## File Layout

```
arxiv-rag/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Dockerfile
в”ңв”Җв”Җ docker-compose.yml
в”ңв”Җв”Җ requirements.txt
в”ңв”Җв”Җ .env.example
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ config/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ settings.py          # Pydantic settings (reads .env)
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ celery_config.py     # All Celery knobs
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ logging.py           # structlog JSON / console
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ celery_app/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ main.py              # App factory, queue topology, Beat schedule
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tasks/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ scrape.py        # Tasks 1вҖ“3  (scrape queue)
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ process.py       # Tasks 4вҖ“5  (process queue)
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ embed.py         # Tasks 6вҖ“7  (embed queue)
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ maintenance.py   # DLQ retry, health check, pdf purge
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ utils/
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ dedup.py         # Redis-backed paper deduplication
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ embedder.py      # OpenAI / local embedding abstraction
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ paper_schema.py  # Pydantic models for inter-task data
в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ text_cleaner.py  # Academic PDF text normalisation
в”Ӯ
в””в”Җв”Җ scripts/
    в””в”Җв”Җ trigger_scrape.py    # CLI to manually kick off ingestion
```

## Connecting Your Vector Store

Open `celery_app/tasks/embed.py` and replace the `_write_chunks()` stub
with your writer. Each chunk arriving there is a plain dict with:

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `chunk_id` | str | `<arxiv_id>_<section_idx>_<chunk_idx>` |
| `arxiv_id` | str | e.g. `2401.12345` |
| `title` | str | Paper title |
| `section` | str | Section heading |
| `text` | str | Chunk body (вүҲ512 tokens) |
| `embedding` | list[float] | Dense vector |
| `embedding_model` | str | e.g. `text-embedding-3-small` |
| `embedding_dim` | int | 1536 (OpenAI) / 384 (local) |
| `page_start` | int | PDF page number |
| `authors` | list[str] | Author names |
| `categories` | list[str] | ArXiv category codes |
| `published` | str | ISO 8601 date |
| `token_count` | int | Approximate token count |
